<p rend="chapter">Kathāvatthu-aṭṭhakathā</p>

<p rend="gatha1">Nisinno <pb ed="P" n="0.0001" /><pb ed="M" n="0.0105" /><pb ed="V" n="0.0100" /> devalokasmiṃ, devasaṅghapurakkhato;</p>

<p rend="gathalast">Sadevakassa lokassa, satthā appaṭipuggalo.</p>

<p rend="gatha1">Sabbapaññattikusalo, paññattiparidīpanaṃ;</p>

<p rend="gathalast">Vatvā puggalapaññattiṃ, loke uttamapuggalo.</p>

<p rend="gatha1">Yaṃ puggalakathādīnaṃ, kathānaṃ vatthubhāvato;</p>

<p rend="gathalast">Kathāvatthuppakaraṇaṃ, saṅkhepena adesayī.</p>

<p rend="gatha1">Mātikāṭhapaneneva <pb ed="V" n="0.0101" />, ṭhapitassa surālaye;</p>

<p rend="gathalast">Tassa moggaliputtena, vibhattassa mahītale.</p>

<p rend="gatha1">Idāni yasmā sampatto, atthasaṃvaṇṇanākkamo;</p>

<p rend="gathalast">Tasmā naṃ vaṇṇayissāmi, taṃ suṇātha samāhitāti.</p>
